@[simp]
theorem aeval_map_algebra_map (x : B) (p : polynomial R) : aeval x (map (algebraMap R A) p) = aeval x p := by
  rw [aeval_def, aeval_def, eval₂_map, IsScalarTower.algebraMap_eq R A B]
#align aeval_map_algebra_map aeval_map_algebra_map
aeval_coe:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `polynomial -/
@[simp]
theorem aeval_coe (S : Subalgebra R A) (x : S) (p : polynomial R) : aeval (x : A) p = aeval x p :=
  aeval_algebraMap_apply A x p
#align aeval_coe aeval_coe
aeval_algebra_map_eq_zero_iff_of_injecti:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `polynomial -/
theorem aeval_algebra_map_eq_zero_iff_of_injective {x : A} {p : polynomial R}
    (h : function.injective (algebraMap A B)) : aeval (algebraMap A B x) p = 0 ↔ aeval x p = 0 := by
  rw [aeval_algebra_map_apply, ← (algebraMap A B).map_zero, h.eq_iff]
#align aeval_algebra_map_eq_zero_iff_of_injective aeval_algebra_map_eq_zero_iff_of_injective
aeval_algebra_map_eq_zero_iff:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `polynomial -/
@[simp]
theorem aeval_algebra_map_eq_zero_iff [NoZeroSMulDivisors A B] [Nontrivial B] (x : A) (p : polynomial R) :
    aeval (algebraMap A B x) p = 0 ↔ aeval x p = 0 := by
  rw [aeval_algebra_map_apply, Algebra.algebraMap_eq_smul_one, smul_eq_zero, iff_false_intro (one_ne_zero' B),
    or_false_iff]
#align aeval_algebra_map_eq_zero_iff aeval_algebra_map_eq_zero_iff
aeval_algebra_map_apply:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `polynomial -/
theorem aeval_algebra_map_apply (x : A) (p : polynomial R) : aeval (algebraMap A B x) p = algebraMap A B (aeval x p) :=
  by rw [aeval_def, aeval_def, hom_eval₂, ← IsScalarTower.algebraMap_eq]
#align aeval_algebra_map_apply aeval_algebra_map_apply
